{"tid":398364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講新一代先香港核心價值崩解元兇","createTime":"2017-09-13T06:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T15:30:03.000Z","uid":102240,"like":2,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6c60da143d7c426b63825c6e3fbe3d2f0d0530","tid":398364,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"講真，香港本身就有原居民，即係你講既牛屎佬<br />\n<br />\n到移民偷渡湧入香港，成大堆潮州人福建人等等努力生產，即係你口中既蝗，香港先黎度呢代<br />\n<br />\n明明香港就係「牛屎佬」同「蝗」既地方，獅子山精神都係講緊佢地，當年大家都有份炒股炒樓，講愛國講回歸，無講公投無講獨立<br />\n<br />\n係新一代出到黎，唔知搵唔到食上唔到樓定乜，先攬住香港核心價值黎講，香港被建立果陣，你精蟲都未成形呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都好同情你搵唔到食上唔到樓，咁應該係針住經濟黎講，唔係乜都泛政治化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe72cdaf550c5581f266e572a32647789db1112d","tid":398364,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"正經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3133cd62829b08200940e8f2f5a000747309de6","tid":398364,"uid":55657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"35c4546f0770d576df48642098a69e24ee522ae5","tid":398364,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閱</blockquote><br />\n你點定義香港人？"},{"pid":"cacc3eff3e0ba5c3e3b4a0d38df9d4868e448b90","tid":398364,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"香港核心價值係一個字, 錢<br />\n<br />\n亦從來冇崩解過,<br />\n<br />\n即使當日佔中,大家都照返工"},{"pid":"d9e56f7878f9e7bbf15d9a6f384bc8d75ab61e4e","tid":398364,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港核心價值係一個字, 錢<br />\n<br />\n亦從來冇崩解過,<br />\n<br />\n即使當日佔中,大家都照返工</blockquote><br />\n所以你提咩普世價值先係少數"},{"pid":"6fbe22628c64a7214e7c1b131a51a51554d827d3","tid":398364,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score